{"tid":382961,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩槍game好鍾意幫人睇屎忽/睇位？","createTime":"2017-09-01T06:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T08:09:20.000Z","uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"537afeb2028142e95e584b39e110b8fbb416c2e0","tid":382961,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"例如pubg咁 一隊squad唔可以全部都做晒攻擊 除非打到最後<br />\n4個裡面一個係主要攻擊 一個係幫打 一個係確認敵人位置 一個係睇屎忽 (我唔知巴打會唔會係咁打 但我會係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意例如自己隊友集中打緊一邊嘅時候 我會搵個地方攞視野 去留意附近會唔會有其他人+確認佢地位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當隊友慢慢打前時  因為我已經confirm左附近無人 可以放心行 如果有人 就清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而csgo就唔洗講啦 屎忽一定要睇 但炸彈記住要掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打都鍾意做啲附助性嘅位置/角色？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附助唔代表廢 只係比較鍾意照顧好隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1465b32b179e96d31c3f632464f63e8f34ec4dba","tid":382961,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"出街好鍾意睇人屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcfa34592b272e30d407c4167452cbee058a0b0","tid":382961,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"終於有人明白我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8cac5c6ce4d37570bb588b191d9adf11fee1f2","tid":382961,"uid":21664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"通常依D位叫基佬"},{"pid":"8d9ed60f8f89837b68b0c9af6deca5704315dd6e","tid":382961,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":